description:
Thanks to Micro Center for helping me make this video, especially to the many employees and manager (hi Jeff!) who were so accomodating and helpful!

The products I purchased from Micro Center for this guide include:

  - Raspberry Pi 5 4GB: https://www.microcenter.com/product/673712/raspberry-pi-5-4gb-lpddr4x
  - Raspberry Pi Mouse: https://www.microcenter.com/product/613559/raspberry-pi-official-raspberry-pi-optical-usb-mouse-black-grey
  - Raspberry Pi Keyboard: https://www.microcenter.com/product/613557/raspberry-pi-official-usb-keyboard-with-usb-hub-black-gray
  - Raspberry Pi 27W USB-C Power Supply: https://www.microcenter.com/product/671926/raspberry-pi-27w-usb-c-psu-white
  - Micro Center 256GB Premium microSD card: https://www.microcenter.com/product/657911/micro-center-premium-256gb-microsdxc-card-uhs-i-flash-memory-card-c10-u3-v30-a1-micro-sd-card-with-adapter
  - Micro Connectors Acrylic Stackable Pi Case: https://www.microcenter.com/product/658280/micro-connectors-acrylic
title: Raspberry Pi 5: Getting Started
